######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

start_at = far_1_tavern
start_theme = my_theme
themes {
   my_theme : theme {
      theme_settings {
         losegame_jingle = on
         success_jingle  = on
         wingame_jingle  = on
         failure_jingle  = off
      }
   }
}
######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################
loading_screen = pixel_templedao
on_startup {
   
   : print "This is a text based adventure game. Type in commands to perform actions, solve pussles and progress the story.\n TIPS \n -typing 'EXAMINE' followed by an object name usually provides more info on that object \n -typing 'INVENTORY' shows you a list of things you are currently carrying \n -typing 'SAVE' saves your game \n -typing 'LOAD' will load a saved game";
   : press_any_key ;
   : ask_string question = "Before we begin...What is your name?"  var = "name" ;
   
}
######################################
#  Strings                           #
######################################

strings {
   
   name : string "" ;
   
}
######################################
#  Locations                         #
######################################

locations {

   far_1_tavern : location "" ;
   far_2_tavern : location "" ;
   outside_tavern : location "" ;
   inside_tavern : location "" ;
   toilet : location "" ;
   
}

######################################
#  Connections                       #
######################################

connections {

   from, direction, to = [
     // outside_apothecary, north, road_1,
     // apothecary, north, road_2, 
     // far_1_tavern, north, far_2_tavern, 
     // far_2_tavern, north, outside_tavern, 
      ]
   
}

######################################
#  Objects                           #
######################################

objects {
   
   painting : scenery "a haunting painting" ;
   stools : scenery "typical bar stools" ;
   cloak_woman : scenery "a woman in a cloak" ;
   bartender : scenery "the bartender" ;
   ancient_key : object "an ancient key" ;
   red_drink : object "a red drink" ;
   blue_drink : object "a blue drink" ;
   green_drink : object "a green drink" ;
   yellow_drink : object "a yellow drink" ;
   purple_drink : object "a purple drink" ;
   
   
    
   
}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {
  
//describe far from tavern
      : if (is_at "far_1_tavern") {
      : print "You open your eyes. The surrounding looks unfamiliar. It is nighttime." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "The air is curiously still and fills your mouth with a stale taste.  It’s too quiet, and not a single creature of the night stirs. The only thing breaking the silence is the incessant ringing in your ears..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "“What happened? Where is this place?" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Darkness seeps out of the night. You can see nothing except...a faint glow to the north \n Looks like you have no choice but to walk towards it" ;
      }
      
//describe far from tavern
      : if (is_at "far_2_tavern") {
      : print "You're getting closer to the glow. You can make out an outline of a building of some sort." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "You sigh with relief...at least there is civilisation here. Better keep walking" ;
      }  
      
//describe outside tavern
      : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : print "You seem to be standing in front of a door leading into what looks like an apothecarium..or is it a tavern? " ;
      }
   
//describe inside tavern
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "You look around and start to wonder what kind of room you are even in. To your right, you notice a PAINTING hanging on the wall. To your left, a bar with two open STOOLS. A narrow door at the back probably leads to the BATHROOM.";
      : print "A WOMAN in a cloak is sitting at the bar. She is drinking a shimmery beverage. There is a MAN in a dark robe behind the bar. The shelf behind the bar is filled with vials, tinctures, bottles, artifacts, scrolls, books, and a lot of things you don’t have a word for.";
      }
   
//describe inside toilet
      : if (is_at "toilet") {
      : print "a regular bathroom stall. Complete with a sink, toilet bowl and lots of scribblings on the wall";
      }
  

}

######################################
#  Booleans                          #
######################################

booleans {
   
   is_key_exists : boolean;
   is_intro_done : boolean;
   is_sitting : boolean;
   
 
}



######################################
#  Integers                          #
######################################

integers {
   
   question_1 : integer "0" ;
   drinking : integer "0" ;
   drunkeness : integer "0" ;
   toilet_writing : integer "0" ;
   
}



######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################


######################################
#  Subroutines                       #
######################################

subroutines {
//game over
   end_game : subroutine {
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : print "YOU DIED" ;
      : failure ;
      : lose_game;
         }
}
######################################
#  On Tick                           #
######################################

on_tick {
//apothecarium ambient
   : if (is_just_entered () ) {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
         : play_music sound="ambient_apothecarium";
      }
      
   }

//if too long far_tavern
   : if (is_at "far_1_tavern" || is_at "far_2_tavern" ) {
      : if (linger() == 3) {
      : print "It's too dark to do anything else out here...maybe you should go towards the light" ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 5) {
      : print "Maybe you should use your feet to WALK there..." ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 6) {
      : print "Stay out here too much longer and you will freeze to death. WALK NORTH already" ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 8) {
      : print "You are lost outside. The night goes cold. Your hands start to shiver. Your mind begins to fade." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "If you found this first puzzle too hard...I hate to break it to you, but this is only the tutorial" ;
      : gosub "end_game";
      : failure ;
      
      }
   }

//if too long outside_tavern
   : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : if (linger() == 6) {
      : print "It's too dark to do anything else out here...maybe you should go inside" ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 8) {
      : print "Maybe you should do something to that DOOR you see before you..." ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 9) {
      : print "Stay out here too much longer and you will freeze to death. OPEN the DOOR already" ;
      }
      : if (linger() == 10) {
      : print "You linger outside the building. The night goes cold. Your hands start to shiver. Your mind begins to fade." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "Perhaps this is for the best. Afterall, a templar who lacks the knowledge to operate a simple door is not worthy of the rewards within" ;
      : gosub "end_game" ;
      : failure ;
      }
   }
}

######################################
#  On Command                        #
######################################

on_command {

//walk any other direction
: match " s _;e _;w _; go back"  {
      : if (is_at "far_1_tavern" || is_at "far_2_tavern") {
      : print "It's too dark to go that way" ;
      }
}


//walk forward once
: match "walk forward; go forward; n _"  {
      : if (is_at "far_1_tavern") {
      : print "You make haste towards the light..." ;
      : goto "far_2_tavern" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}

//walk forward twice
: match "walk forward; go forward; keep walking; n _"  {
      : if (is_at "far_2_tavern") {
      : print "You make haste towards the light..." ;
      : goto "outside_tavern" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}

//enter tavern
: match "open door; enter _ "  {
      : if (is_at "outside_tavern") {
      : print "Nothing else to do but go inside..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : goto "inside_tavern" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}
//inside tavern - misc
: match "examine vial; examine tincture; examine bottle; examine artifact; examine scrolls; examine books"  {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "You strain your eyes but can't make out anything useful there" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}
: match "examine bar"  {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "a worn out bar" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}
: match "examine stool"  {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "look's comfortable enough..." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}
: match "examine bathroom; examine toilet"  {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "look's like a regular bathroom from here...smells like one too." ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
}

   : print "Drinks here don't look like anything you've seen before..." ;
}

: match "drink drink; down drink; gulp drink; take drink"  {
   : if (is_exists "red_drink") {
      : print "You down the red drink in one go" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : print "The taste was all over the place. Sweet, bitter, floral, earthy and a bit like cardboard. It can only be described as...chaotic" ;
      : increment "drunkeness" ;
      : destroy "red_drink" ;
   }
}

      : if (is_key_exists == true && drunkeness == 5) {
      : print "You reach out to touch the key and...you manage to grab the key. You are a little shocked. This should be impossible! Was it the drinks? No one else seemed to notice, so you quickly pocket the key" ;
      : set_boolean var = "is_key_exists"  value = "false" ;
      : pocket "ancient_key" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      }
      : if (is_key_exists == true && drunkeness != 5) {
      : print "You reach out to touch the key and...nothing happens. You are not sure why you did that..maybe you need a drink..." ;
      }
      }
      }

//enter bathroom
: match "enter bathroom; enter toilet; go bathroom; go toilet"  {
      : if (is_at "inside_tavern") {
      : print "you walk to the back and enter the bathroom" ;
      : goto "toilet" ;
      : press_any_key ;
      : redescribe;
      }
   }
//read writings in toilet
: match "read writing; examine writing; look writing"  {
      : if (is_at "toilet") {
         : cycle predictable_order = "false"  key = "toilet_event" {
         : print "One of the writings say \n <Do not paper-mache the toilet. And don't get forget to Flush!<2>> " ;
         : print "Further down someone else wrote\n <What's a flush?<2>>" ;
         : print "Further donw someone else wrote \n <It's what comes after a Full House<2>>" ;   
         : print "On another wall it says \n <Please send pictures of your feet to xxxxxx<2>> \n the number seems to be scratched out " ;
         : print "" ;
         
         }
      
      }
   }


      
      
}
